{"id": 2381, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心×丹麦】哪一刻你觉得一个人的“童心”还没死？", "description": "童心和年龄有关吗？哪些时刻你觉得有童心感？在童话王国丹麦旅行能找回被遗忘的童心吗？", "record_count": 5734, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180529165317SaF1xdHjZPWvDmiu.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-30T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 284416, "content": "嗯？这是炸乐高粉的吧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115890}, {"id": 284417, "content": "参与这个讨论的人吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 288, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359326}, {"id": 284929, "content": "能长期保持一个爱好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923997}, {"id": 284418, "content": "犯二", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 284419, "content": "童心就是我们要去看鲸鱼!", "image": "img/option/option/20180530112757mnbteAdkW27jMCcQ", "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359325}, {"id": 284420, "content": "偶尔也会一个人去电影院看动画片啊\n比如六一马上上映的哆啦A梦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333517}, {"id": 284676, "content": "看到小玩意会不自觉的拨弄几下", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318209}, {"id": 284421, "content": "不做作", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966594}, {"id": 284677, "content": "情不自禁的一个恶作剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359854}, {"id": 284933, "content": "比如看到铜锣烧一定会买，因为哆啦A梦最喜欢吃这个，感觉好好吃的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360678}, {"id": 285189, "content": "还在想象自己会飞\n", "image": "img/option/option/201806021912140ZvmsAPhMUwrYKcL.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1361933}, {"id": 284422, "content": "看到小昆虫还是想拿起棍子戳一戳", "image": null, "praise_count": 110, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355575}, {"id": 284678, "content": "在地铁上遇见小孩子就忍不住逗一逗 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359850}, {"id": 284423, "content": "高兴的时候想蹦蹦跳跳地向前走", "image": null, "praise_count": 837, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327120}, {"id": 284424, "content": "愿意花时间做一些无意义的小事", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 858761}, {"id": 289032, "content": "爱热闹、爱玩闹、颜控，喜欢美的事物，有时候肤浅大概也是一种童心", "image": "img/option/option/20180625063419VdFBJZCyKrAwlIi1.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382874}, {"id": 284425, "content": "到乐高乐园穷玩啊！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218882}, {"id": 284426, "content": "永远不浸淫在大苦大悲中，对不美好随时准备忘记", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350895}, {"id": 284938, "content": "捧起相机的时候。", "image": "img/option/option/20180531223347oYU9lSFkNLc25DE7.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1308712}, {"id": 352266, "content": "怎么没有评论?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1679797}, {"id": 285708, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366392}, {"id": 352268, "content": "学了很多高端的东西,却只想用它去实现一些很简单的想法(本人)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1679797}, {"id": 284429, "content": "叫我妈给我掏耳朵哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1233271}, {"id": 284430, "content": "但是我觉得跟年龄无关，我会把房间装饰成浪漫风，我们宿舍床铺是上床下桌格式。床头挂满DIY照片，绕上星星灯，圆形淡蓝色蚊帐洒下来，一排娃娃机抓的公仔，打开音响放些轻音乐，还有哆啦A梦投影灯照射在墙壁上旋转，坐在各种动物拼接的地垫上吃着零食，刷着手机。简直。。。。。。。太放松了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359338}, {"id": 284432, "content": "会因为桃花开了而开心 因为天空清澈而开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 213, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245394}, {"id": 284433, "content": "坐火车喜欢看窗外的风景", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1233271}, {"id": 286737, "content": "看到这个标题进来的人，童心应该都还在吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366483}, {"id": 284434, "content": "会忍不住跳着下台阶", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800698}, {"id": 284435, "content": "想起了有网友说的她那个，在商场给玩偶娃娃捋刘海的大高个男朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318017}, {"id": 284436, "content": "喜欢圣诞节", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 284437, "content": "和小侄子争论可不可以悔棋的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317854}, {"id": 284694, "content": "我陪女儿看了三年的亲宝儿歌了\n有一次点美团 要求店主给我画一个小猪佩奇", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359887}, {"id": 284439, "content": "依然会去户外放风筝，陪伴小朋友玩一些小游戏（不是电子游戏）。", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1331607}, {"id": 284695, "content": "对喜欢的人，会不畏惧年龄", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729414}, {"id": 284440, "content": "看哆啦A梦《伴我同行》，在电影院哭成sb", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686345}, {"id": 284696, "content": "一辈子离不开动漫。在这个国家就是幼稚的象征。。。没办法", "image": "img/option/option/20180530232602fCK9g52lnQY0kJTs.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 285208, "content": "会和小玩偶对话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362189}, {"id": 284441, "content": "刚睡醒松松软软的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312238}, {"id": 284697, "content": "喜欢小奶狗???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 288793, "content": "逛超市赖在玩具区不肯走", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991013}, {"id": 284442, "content": "喜欢儿童玩具", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251935}, {"id": 284698, "content": "下雨的时候，我自己会很开心地在没人的地方拿着雨伞转圈圈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291669}, {"id": 284443, "content": "90年的我现在还保持着看《柯南》的喜欢～", "image": "img/option/option/20180530115416miGPh9dVbg8t0TJy.jpg", "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359360}, {"id": 284444, "content": "和她一起的每一刻，她都有着一颗童心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1306225}, {"id": 284445, "content": "看热血动漫 依然像个傻-逼的时候                  十年饮冰 难凉热血", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 857098}, {"id": 284701, "content": "喜欢各种玩具", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855480}, {"id": 284190, "content": "在厨房一边做饭一边跟手里的食材说抱歉", "image": null, "praise_count": 346, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 284446, "content": "还玩玩具", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989247}, {"id": 284191, "content": "会跟亲密的人日常拌嘴，或者开玩笑、整蛊恶作剧来寻开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 509, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 284192, "content": "公共场合也会做点傻事，经过小猫小狗会停下来逗一逗，甚至“对话”两句", "image": null, "praise_count": 942, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}]}